aptcron (0.0.9) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix IndexError on new packages/packages that are to be deleted.
  * Account for newly installed, removed and downgraded packages.
  * Print filename and exception line in catchall-statements.
  * Minor pep8 coding standard fixes.

 -- Mathias Ertl <mati@er.tl>  Mon, 09 Jun 2014 19:43:12 +0200

